" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 609px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Recording of visual evoked potentials",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 589px; height: 317px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    A schematic diagram presents the steps in recording of visual evoked potentials. Each alternation of the checkerboard pattern is followed by amplification of the electrical activity and conversion of the analog signal to digital form (A-D conversion). Signals of repeated visual stimuli are averaged to reduce the effect of random electrical noise.",
